import { Typography } from "@mui/material"
import {FullScreenContainer ,StyledPaper ,StyledTypography ,StyledForm,StyledInput,StyledText
  ,StyledTextField,StyledBottomText,StyledLink,StyledButton} from "../common/loginsignupstyles"
import { ReactComponent as Logo } from '../images/Logo_with_text.svg'
export const Signup=()=>{
    return <FullScreenContainer>
          <StyledPaper>
            <Typography sx={{
              textAlign:"center",
              fontSize:"1.75rem",
              fontWeight:"700",
              fontFamily:"Baikal, Inter, sans-serif",
              letterSpacing:"-0.025em"
            }}>
              Get Started
            </Typography>
             <Typography sx={{
              textAlign:"center",
              fontSize:"13px",

             }}>
             Please enter your details to create your account
             </Typography>

          </StyledPaper>

    </FullScreenContainer>
    
    
}
